  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You order your vectors to twist the limps of a creature you can see within range. Make a ranged ninjutsu attack, dealing 5d10 necrotic damage on a hit. Also on a hit, choose between an arm or leg:</p><ul><li>Arm: the target must make a constitution saving throw, on a failed save, it drops whatever is holding, unable to use that hand until the end of your next turn.</li><li>Leg: the target must make a constituion saving throw, on a failed save, it falls prone unable to stand up until the end of your next turn.</li></ul><p>If you use this jutsu against a creature you have <strong>lifted</strong>, you may give yourself advantage on the attack roll or give it disadvantage against the saving throw, and the condition ends.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks</strong>: For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, the damage by 1d10, and the number of targets by 1.</p>",
